@ConditionalOnExpression("${solver.parallelExecutor}") public class ConcurrentExecutor<S extends Solution<S,I>,I extends Instance> extends Executor<S,I>
Concurrent executor, execute multiple runs in parallel for a given instance-algorithm pair
